{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7dc47d90cf","title":"致中原局、鄂西北区党委、鄂院边地委诺同志电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"af21a02ed3","index":0,"year":1946,"month":9,"day":10,"articleId":"7dc47d90cf"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji22","name":"毛泽东全集第22卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji22.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji22":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"83110f49b5","type":"paragraph","text":"致中原局、鄂西北区党委、鄂院边地委诺同志电！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"7dc47d90cf"},{"id":"5fd26ac345","type":"paragraph","text":"1946年9月10日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"7dc47d90cf"},{"id":"90e715421c","type":"paragraph","text":"在陵南、鄂西、鄂中、鄂东对付我中原军者共十四个旅，分属胡宗南、程潜、刘崎三人指挥。我中原军的任务就是胶紧牙关，克服困难，在当地立稳脚跟，创立根据地，钳制这十四个旅，协助老解放区粉碎国民党进攻。你们过去两个多月英勇斗争已起了极大的战略作用，中央希望并责成你们今后还要起同样的作用，全党全军均关心你们，你们不是孤立的。[1]这是毛泽东关于通报各地战况为中共中央起草的致中原局、鄂西北区党委、鄂统边地委诸同志电的主要内容。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"7dc47d90cf"}],"page":{"id":"329d4e00e8","publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"7dc47d90cf","start":152,"end":152}}}},"__N_SSG":true}